  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个时序图，展示用户通过调度应用管理事件和提醒的完整流程。核心场景有三个：添加事件、设置提醒、查看当日事件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "SchedulerApp",
        "Event",
        "Reminder"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我注意到事件和提醒需要持久化，是不是要引入EventDAO和ReminderService来处理数据层？另外，这些IoT工业相关的实体——TelemetryStream、PLC_Logic、ActuatorController、EdgeNode——是作为参数还是独立参与者？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EventDAO",
        "ReminderService",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，EventDAO和ReminderService作为数据服务层。那些IoT实体是业务参数，不是独立参与者，它们会出现在方法调用里。比如创建事件时传入TelemetryStream，持久化时用PLC_Logic。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EventDAO",
        "ReminderService",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主流程。用户向SchedulerApp发起添加事件请求，SchedulerApp创建Event对象并传入TelemetryStream，然后Event调用EventDAO的add_event方法，参数是PLC_Logic。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "SchedulerApp",
        "Event",
        "EventDAO",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "这个流向是对的。EventDAO处理完后要返回确认给SchedulerApp，用虚线箭头表示异步回调。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EventDAO",
        "SchedulerApp"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加。现在处理提醒流程：用户请求设置提醒，SchedulerApp创建Reminder对象，这里我传入ActuatorController作为参数，然后Reminder调用ReminderService的schedule_reminder，参数用EdgeNode。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "SchedulerApp",
        "Reminder",
        "ReminderService",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
