      "utterance": "完成。我检查一遍：添加事件用了TelemetryStream和PLC_Logic，设置提醒用了ActuatorController和EdgeNode，查看事件用了ActuatorController。所有响应都用虚线箭头，参与者有User、SchedulerApp、Event、EventDAO、Reminder、ReminderService。",
      "elements_involved": [
